# Mobile App Rules

## Animations & Gestures

Reanimated v4 -- these are REMOVED and will crash:
- `useAnimatedGestureHandler` -- use `Gesture.Pan()` + `GestureDetector`
- `useAnimatedScrollHandler` -- use `useScrollViewOffset`

```tsx
// CORRECT (Reanimated v4 + gesture-handler v2)
import { Gesture, GestureDetector } from 'react-native-gesture-handler';

const pan = Gesture.Pan()
  .onUpdate((e) => { translateY.value = e.translationY; })
  .onEnd(() => { translateY.value = withSpring(0); });

<GestureDetector gesture={pan}>
  <Animated.View />
</GestureDetector>
```

## Forbidden Imports

- `expo-blur` -- not installed, crashes on import
- `useAnimatedGestureHandler` from `react-native-reanimated` -- removed in v4
- `PanGestureHandler` from `react-native-gesture-handler` -- deprecated, use `Gesture.Pan()` + `GestureDetector`

## Mapbox

- Use `MapboxGL.MarkerView` for custom markers (live RN view, sharp rendering)
- Do NOT use `MapboxGL.PointAnnotation` for custom views (rasterizes to blurry bitmap)
- `BuildingsLayer` sourceID="composite" may not exist in all styles -- wrap in try/catch

## Safe Area

Every screen and bottom sheet must use `useSafeAreaInsets()` for top/bottom padding.
Never hardcode pixel values for notch or home indicator spacing.

## Common Modal

Use `src/components/common/Modal.tsx` for bottom sheets. It handles safe area, spring animation, and backdrop dismiss automatically. Do not create inline RN `Modal` with manual overlay styles.
